snippet.title: DEAD ALLIANCE - Multiplayer Trailer [OPEN BETA UK]
snippet.description:
Good morning future zombies! You're invited to play the Multiplayer Open Beta June 27-June 31.  http://www.deadalliance.com

Participate in three intense game modes – Team Deathmatch, King of the Hill, and the MOBA-inspired Attrition mode – across three zombie-plagued maps.

Like on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/DeadAllianceMG
Follow on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/DeadAllianceMG
